n coffee table with a TV and Xbox in the background. A PlayStation controller sits in front of the console.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[PlayStation 5]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Zoom now says it won’t use any customer content for AI training]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>在本周早些时候遭到强烈反对后，Zoom（再次）改变了方向并更新了服务条款。最近，其条款更新似乎赋予了该平台<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/zoom-reverses-policy-that-allowed-it-to-train-ai-on-customer-data-212230598.html">无限的能力，可以使用客户数据</a>来训练人工智能模型，继消费者对该条款的强烈反对之后，该公司现在表示，不会使用任何消费者数据来训练来自 Zoom 或第三方的人工智能模型。之前的措辞表示，“未经客户同意”，它不会这样做，这引起了人们的注意，因为“同意”（充其量）对于加入会议组织者启用的通话（并确认弹出窗口）的人来说是一个灰色地带。该功能并已同意条款。</p><p> Zoom 的更改列在其<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://blog.zoom.us/zooms-term-service-ai/">之前博客文章的</a>序言更新中。 “根据收到有关 Zoom 最近更新的服务条款的反馈，特别是与我们新的生成人工智能功能相关的反馈，Zoom 更新了我们的服务条款和以下博客文章，以明确 Zoom 不会使用您的任何音频、视频、聊天、屏幕共享、附件或其他通信，例如客户内容（例如民意调查结果、白板和反应），以训练 Zoom 或第三方人工智能模型，”通知中写道。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>事实上，Zoom 服务条款中之前麻烦的第 10 条（与人工智能和消费者数据相关）也发生了变化。 “Zoom 不会使用您的任何音频、视频、聊天、屏幕共享、附件或其他通信类客户内容（例如投票结果、白板和反应）来训练 Zoom 或第三方人工智能模型，”更新版本读。即使 Zoom 针对反弹做出了让步，该部分的先前版本仍添加了“未经客户同意”的短语。但由于“同意”似乎只需参加一次会议（甚至可能是你工作所需的一次会议）并确认弹出窗口即可获得，因此一些用户认为这是一个潜在的偷偷摸摸的漏洞，可以在人们没有太多信息的情况下收集人工智能数据选择。新版本消除了这种歧义。</p><p> “我们更新了我们的服务条款（第 10 条），以进一步确认 Zoom 不会使用您的任何音频、视频、聊天、屏幕共享、附件或其他通信，例如客户内容（例如投票结果、白板）和反应）来训练 Zoom 或第三方人工智能模型，”Hashim 在修改后的博客文章中表示。 “此外，我们还更新了产品内的通知以反映这一点。”</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/zoom-now-says-it-wont-use-any-customer-content-for-ai-training-170533411.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/zoom-now-says-it-wont-use-any-customer-content-for-ai-training-170533411.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> a65dafc2-20a5-433b-84c6-cf9b4fd1707d</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 11 Aug 2023 17:05:33 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691773061</ingested><modified> 2023-08-11T16:57:45+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="2684" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/8fd75e60-3866-11ee-bcbf-0bd7dc42ba84" width="4026"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2684" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/8fd75e60-3866-11ee-bcbf-0bd7dc42ba84" width="4026"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ASSOCIATED PRESS]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[A woman works at Zoom headquarters on Friday, Feb. 3, 2023, in San Jose, Calif. Zoom is asking employees who live within a 50-mile radius of its offices to work onsite two days a week. (AP Photo/Haven Daley)]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Zoom Return to Office]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Chip implants get under your skin so you can leave your keys at home]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>软件工程师 Miana Windall 的皮下植入了大约 25 个植入物，从磁铁到 RFID 技术。虽然如果你胆怯的话，这可能会让你起鸡皮疙瘩，但“在大多数情况下，它们并不真正引人注目，”她告诉 Engadget。在周四的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://forum.defcon.org/node/246100">DEF CON 安全会议</a>上，温德尔谈到了她如何对植入物产生兴趣，以及她对植入物进行编程以供个人使用的经验，例如扫描她以前的办公楼。</p><p> RFID 技术为地铁卡或感应支付等可扫描技术提供支持。这项相对简单的技术<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.rfidjournal.com/the-history-of-rfid-technology#:~:text=Mario%20W.,a%20door%20without%20a%20key.">于 20 世纪 70 年代首次获得专利</a>，而车身改造的历史可以追溯到几千年前。 Windall 说，尽管如此，RFID 植入仍然没有充分发挥其潜力，对很多人来说它们仍然是一个噱头。但如果你想去泡吧而不带包，你可以购买合适款式的锁，并植入一个不会丢失的传感器，以便扫描进出你的家。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>不过，它们并不是魔法。 “芯片植入的工作原理并不像好莱坞电影那样，”生物黑客和植入服务 Dangerous Things 的创始人 Amal Graafstra 告诉 Engadget。 “当附近没有读者时，他们甚至不活跃、不活跃、不精力充沛”</p><p>这意味着 RFID 植入物的使用范围相当有限，而且它主要是一项基础技术，你必须能够破解它才能发挥作用。开箱即用的用例有限，例如可以让您启动汽车的<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://dangerousthings.com/product/teslaflex/">特斯拉钥匙卡植入</a>，但通常用户必须能够自己将某些关键配置复制到上面。 “当我们出售应答器时，我们出售的是钥匙，而不是锁，”格拉夫斯特拉说。用户必须具备一定的技术头脑才能制作“锁”。</p><p>在去身体改造艺术家或穿孔师那里植入芯片之前，了解这一点很有帮助，否则您最终可能会得到无法使用的芯片。 “在手术前进行研究并尽可能确定你想要什么，”温德尔说。不过，温德尔本人确实有一些不活跃的物质，保留在皮肤下是无害的。</p><p>公司现在也在寻找使用 RFID 植入物作为安全工具的方法。 RFID 技术存在一个固有的漏洞，因为它要求访问凭证容易被盗。但将这些凭证作为植入物至少可以防止有人轻易窃取您的门禁卡或信息。</p><p> “有人在你不知情的情况下扫描你的凭证的可能性可能没有那么高，”温德尔说。 “你的手不可能被扒窃，至少在没有砍刀的情况下是不可能的。”</p><p>此外，随着身份验证对于防止未经授权的帐户访问变得更加重要，这些植入程序可用于证明您的身份。随着公司希望<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/passkeys-passwords-authentication-security-133024414.html">用密钥取代双因素身份验证</a>，将这些凭据放在你的皮肤下是可能的。 Graafstra 表示，你的密钥可以上传到可以验证你身份的芯片植入物，而不是可能丢失的硬件密钥或可能被欺骗的短信验证。</p><p> RFID 植入物不需要 FDA 批准，因为它们不是医疗设备。科罗拉多大学博尔德分校媒体学院教授<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/32426543/">Harsha Gangadharbatla</a>博士表示，虽然它们看起来总体上安全可靠，但仍有一些风险因素需要考虑。</p><p>他在给 Engadget 的电子邮件中表示：“消费者应该充分意识到与此类技术相关的‘隐性’成本（隐私、风险和广告信息），而不仅仅是获得此类植入的成本。”</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/chip-implants-get-under-your-skin-so-you-can-leave-your-keys-at-home-170008199.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/chip-implants-get-under-your-skin-so-you-can-leave-your-keys-at-home-170008199.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> ab38275d-9236-493c-a185-8f2811c8c0ad</guid><dc:creator>凯蒂·马龙</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 11 Aug 2023 17:00:08 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691772198</ingested><modified> 2023-08-11T16:43:24+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Katie Malone]]></category><media:content height="4000" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/f22e0010-37c5-11ee-aeff-3e5e65c5cad0" width="6000"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="4000" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/f22e0010-37c5-11ee-aeff-3e5e65c5cad0" width="6000"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Казаков Анатолий Павлович via Getty Images]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[implantation of a chip under the human skin. microchips are connected to the fingers of the hand. concept of future technologies aimed at tracking and identifying people.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[implantation of a chip under the human skin. microchips are connected to the fingers of the hand. concept of future technologies aimed at tracking and identifying people.]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Bose QuietComfort Ultra headphones and earbuds are reportedly on the way]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.mysmartprice.com/gear/bose-quietcomfort-ultra-quietcomfort-ultra-earbuds-first-look-revealed-exclusive/"><ins>据</ins><em><ins>MySmartPrice 透露，Bose 正准备推出一些新的耳机和耳塞，这是 QuietComfort 系列的更新。</ins></em></a> <em>&nbsp;</em> Bose QuietComfort Ultra 耳塞将是<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/bose-quietcomfort-earbuds-2-review-130026306.html"><ins>广受好评的 QuietComfort Earbuds II 的</ins></a>继任者，而 QuietComfort Ultra 耳机看起来是该公司<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/bose-quietcomfort-45-review-143031637.html"><ins>QuietComfort 45 耳机的更优质产品。</ins></a></p><p>所有 Bose 产品（尤其是 QuietComfort II 耳塞）的亮点之一就是主动降噪功能。该公司的 ANC 技术是无与伦比的，这些新产品无疑提供了这一技术。这两款新产品均提供完全集成的 ANC 技术，因此您可以在下次飞行时安全地忽略旁边的人。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>除了 ANC 之外，QuietComfort Ultra 耳塞还配备了各种柔软的耳塞，其外观设计与其前身相似。它们有黑色或白色可供选择，并应包括内置麦克风、触摸控制、蓝牙 v5.3 支持、IPX4 防水等。 Bose 尚未正式宣布这些，因此一些规格仍处于保密状态。 </p><figure><img src="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/11de7cb0-3865-11ee-b9fb-a9fd2636be78" style="height:1246px;width:2385px;" alt="两个耳机的图像。" data-uuid="f58c0aa2-9eb5-3dc2-89f8-f9a1d8d2c2df"><figcaption></figcaption><div class="photo-credit">我的智能价格</div></figure><p>Bose QuietComfort Ultra 耳机也有黑色或白色可供选择，配有物理按钮来调节音量和控制音乐，与 QuietComfort 系列中的其他产品类似。还有一个用于充电和有线连接的 USB-C 端口，其时尚的设计让人想起<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-08-16-bose-700-headphones-review.html"><ins>深受喜爱的 Bose 700 系列耳机。</ins></a></p><p>请记住，这些都是来自信誉良好的第三方的泄密，因此 Bose 尚未公布定价或供货情况。然而， <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.dealabs.com/magazine/bose-quietcomfort-prix-noms-et-coloris-ne-manquez-pas-nos-informations-exclusives-a-propos-des-prochains-casques-et-ecouteurs-26781"><em><ins>Dealabs</ins></em><ins>最近的一份报告</ins></a>表明 QuietComfort Ultra 耳塞的售价约为 380 美元，QuietComfort Ultra 耳机的售价为 550 美元。至于供货情况，Bose 倾向于在 9 月发布新产品线，因此请期待届时发布。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/bose-quietcomfort-ultra-headphones-and-earbuds-are-reportedly-on-the-way-165508108.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/bose-quietcomfort-ultra-headphones-and-earbuds-are-reportedly-on-the-way-165508108.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 18fffa9c-674b-46d4-8576-318a0d701edb</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 11 Aug 2023 16:55:08 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691772909</ingested><modified> 2023-08-11T16:55:13+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Speakers & Headphones]]></category><category><![CDATA[Audio Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="1370" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/f89ecb40-3866-11ee-bdce-162a99d92cb1" width="2062"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1370" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/f89ecb40-3866-11ee-bdce-162a99d92cb1" width="2062"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Billy Steele/Engadget ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Image of Bose QuietComfort 45 headphones.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Bose QC 45]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Rockstar recruits the team behind the biggest ‘GTA V’ roleplay community]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>尽管<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/gta-v/"><em>《侠盗猎车手 V》</em></a>已有近十年的历史，但它仍然是地球上最大的游戏之一。截至撰写本文时，仅 Steam 上就有超过 151,000 人在玩该游戏，它仍然为<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/rockstar-games/">Rockstar Games</a>所有者<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/take-two/">Take-Two 的银行余额</a>做出了重大贡献。</p><p>角色扮演是<em>《GTA V</em> 》经久不衰的重要因素，数以万计的玩家使用模组来创建在圣安地列斯和洛桑托斯更自由地生活、工作和玩耍的角色。现在，Rockstar 正在该领域采取行动，最大的<em>GTA V</em> (FiveM) 和<em>Red Dead Redemption 2</em> (RedM) 模组和社区背后的团队 Cfx.re 已加入发行商。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> “在过去的几年里，我们兴奋地看到 Rockstar 的创意社区找到了扩展<em>Grand Theft Auto V</em>和<em>Red Dead Redemption 2</em>可能性的新方法，特别是通过创建专用的角色扮演服务器，”Rockstar 在其声明中<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/8971o8789584a4/roleplay-community-update">写道</a>。公告。 “作为进一步支持这些努力的一种方式，我们最近扩大了模组政策，正式纳入角色扮演创意社区制作的模组。通过与 Cfx.re 团队合作，我们将帮助他们找到新的方式来支持这个令人难以置信的社区和改善他们为开发者和玩家提供的服务。”</p><p> Cfx.re 的工作人员也对这一举动感到兴奋。该团队<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://forum.cfx.re/t/cfx-re-officially-joins-rockstar-games/5158920">在论坛帖子中写道：</a> “这是我们社区发展的一大进步，也是我们与 Rockstar Games 合作推进 FiveM 平台及其周边创意社区的机会。” “虽然我们的日常运营不会有任何明显的变化，但在 Rockstar 的支持下，我们将继续改进我们的平台，我们对这对我们的用户、社区和创作者意味着什么感到非常兴奋！”</p><p>作为<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.polygon.com/23828445/gta-5-mods-roleplay-red-dead-rockstar-fivem-redm"><em>多边形</em></a><em>&nbsp;</em>据 mod 网站称，周五早上有超过 170,000 名玩家在自定义服务器上使用 FiveM。流行的<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.insider.com/nopixel-grand-theft-auto-v-gta-rp-reddit-xqc-banned-2021-3">NoPixel</a>服务器在 FiveM 上运行，并使用自定义脚本来增强角色扮演体验。</p><p> Rockstar 和 Cfx.re 尚未完全详细说明其针对 FiveM 和 RedM 的计划。无论如何，Rockstar 现在可以用模组为所欲为。它绝对希望继续支持<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/grand-theft-auto-online-pc-exploit-north-192950887.html"><em>GTA 在线模式</em></a><em>&nbsp;</em>及其社区在可预见的未来，但有一个新的侠盗猎车手游戏即将出现的小问题。</p><p>当<em>Grand Theft Auto VI</em>首次亮相时（ <a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/take-two-hints-that-grand-theft-auto-vi-is-coming-in-2024-102507050.html">也许是明年</a>），在 Cfx.re 团队的帮助下，它可能会融入强大的角色扮演功能。因此，Rockstar 有可能通过将<em>GTA VI</em>角色扮演场景纳入游戏并限制模组来完全掌控该场景。公平地说，这只是猜测，但这次收购对未来几年 GTA 角色扮演社区的影响值得考虑。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/rockstar-recruits-the-team-behind-the-biggest-gta-v-roleplay-community-163911086.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/rockstar-recruits-the-team-behind-the-biggest-gta-v-roleplay-community-163911086.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 6ff99dd8-070c-4186-b728-2769dda31c4f</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 11 Aug 2023 16:39:11 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691771991</ingested><modified> 2023-08-11T16:39:56+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Automotive Industry]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="2160" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/0bebc570-3864-11ee-bdf6-b54a8d223283" width="3840"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2160" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/0bebc570-3864-11ee-bdf6-b54a8d223283" width="3840"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Rockstar Games]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Two masked characters hold weapons against a smoky background in Grand Theft Auto V]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Two masked characters hold weapons against a smoky background in Grand Theft Auto V]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Apple TV's MLS Season Pass subscriptions have doubled since Messi's arrival in the US]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>莱昂内尔·梅西 (Lionel Messi) 在美国职业足球大联盟<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/mls/">(Major League Soccer)</a>中崭露头角，并在此过程中提高了<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/apple/">苹果公司的</a>利润。自从几周前他这一代最伟大的足球运动员、可以说是有史以来最好的足球运动员梅西加入球队以来，迈阿密国际队比赛的门票<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.miamiherald.com/sports/mls/inter-miami/article278058137.html">价格一直在飙升</a>。最重要的是，自这位前巴塞罗那和巴黎圣日耳曼球星 7 月份开始在美国打球以来，Apple TV 的<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-tv-mls-season-pass-launch-120017178.html">MLS Season Pass</a>订阅量增加了一倍多。</p><p>这是迈阿密国际队老板之一<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/Jorge__Mas/status/1689758782828556288">豪尔赫·马斯的说法</a>。马斯补充道，“Apple TV 上 MLS Season Pass 的西班牙语收视率已超过 50%，并且还在持续上升”，凸显了这位球员在西班牙语社区的受欢迎程度。苹果首席执行官蒂姆·库克<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/tim_cook/status/1689765138189242368">转发了</a>马斯的评论，表明马斯的说法是真实的（苹果公关团队也一直在关注这条推文）。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="58c056f087464459816cbccf1cdf2a80"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">明天请在<a href="https://twitter.com/AppleTV?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@AppleTV</a>上通过<a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/MLSSeasonPass?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">#MLSSeasonPass</a>观看梅西和所有联赛杯比赛 ⚽️ <a href="https://t.co/ZqmybySBa8">https://t.co/ZqmybySBa8</a></p> — 蒂姆·库克 (@tim_cook) <a href="https://twitter.com/tim_cook/status/1689765138189242368?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2023 年 8 月 10 日</a></blockquote></div><p>该公司尚未透露该服务的订户数量，但 7 月份的报道<a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://9to5mac.com/2023/07/24/mls-season-pass-subscribers-messi/">显示，</a>在梅西到来之前，订户数量已接近 100 万。无论如何，苹果显然对梅西对美国职业足球大联盟季票的影响感到高兴。</p><p>库克在上周的<a data-i13n="cpos:9;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-services-are-making-more-cash-than-ever-but-revenue-shrank-for-the-third-quarter-in-a-row-205545482.html">苹果财报电话会议</a>上<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://seekingalpha.com/article/4623702-apple-inc-aapl-q3-2023-earnings-call-transcript">表示</a>：“对于 MLS 来说，我们对合作关系的进展感到非常满意。” “这显然还处于早期阶段，但我们在订户方面超出了我们的预期，梅西去迈阿密国际的事实对我们有所帮助。所以我们对此感到非常兴奋。”</p><p>苹果将​​下半赛季的订阅<a data-i13n="cpos:10;pos:1" href="https://finance.yahoo.com/news/apple-chops-mls-season-pass-123040467.html">价格从 99 美元降至</a>49 美元，据说每年为 MLS 转播权支付 2.5 亿美元。 <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:ESPN;elmt:;cpos:11;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=8b9dfafd-e7b1-4ac1-bb73-50d55c74d82d&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=ESPN&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAXkH0rrgSXTzYQCmopdTBJXcI-1pCyn02jF99ivGyLzg&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.espn.com%2Fsoccer%2Fstory%2F_%2Fid%2F37975000%2Flionel-messi-mls-apple-adidas-inter-miami" class="rapid-with-clickid">据报道，</a>梅西将从美国职业足球大联盟(MLS)新季通行证订阅者的收入中抽取一部分，作为他与迈阿密国际队合同的一部分。</p><p>梅西在迈阿密已经崭露头角。他在四场比赛中<a data-i13n="cpos:12;pos:1" href="https://www.foxsports.com/stories/soccer/lionel-messi-stats-tracker-every-goal-assist-and-trophy-for-inter-miami">打进</a>7球并贡献3次助攻，迈阿密队全部获胜。在他加盟球队之前，迈阿密热火已经连续11场不胜。</p><p>尽管梅西已经 36 岁了，这个年龄是大多数足球运动员职业生涯的尾声，但梅西仍然很坚强。 <a data-i13n="cpos:13;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/lionel-messi-instagram-record-world-cup-220050247.html?src=rss">去年12月</a>，他带领阿根廷队夺得了世界杯上最大的奖项，并帮助巴黎圣日耳曼队连续赢得法国联赛冠军，然后前往美国。因此，梅西以压倒性优势赢得金球奖，这可以说是足球界最负盛名的个人奖项，并创纪录地第八次获得金球奖。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/apple-tvs-mls-season-pass-subscriptions-have-doubled-since-messis-arrival-in-the-us-150221673.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/apple-tvs-mls-season-pass-subscriptions-have-doubled-since-messis-arrival-in-the-us-150221673.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 9c9b1405-7509-4345-81c1-02e07d2c0ba3</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 11 Aug 2023 15:02:21 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1691767030</ingested><modified> 2023-08-11T15:17:15+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Sports & Recreation]]></category><category><![CDATA[Major League Soccer]]></category><category><![CDATA[Soccer]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="2400" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/0f31d440-385a-11ee-bd7e-821ab31b7e01" width="3600"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="2400" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/0f31d440-385a-11ee-bd7e-821ab31b7e01" width="3600"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[AP Photo/LM Otero]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Inter Miami forward Lionel Messi celebrates a score during penalty kicks in the team's Leagues Cup soccer match against FC Dallas on Sunday, Aug. 6, 2023, in Frisco, Texas.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Leagues Cup Miami Dallas Soccer]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[The best iPhone accessories for 2023]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>新的 Apple iPhone 14 用户应该在拆箱后不久就考虑一下他们想要的新手机配件。与去年的 iPhone 13 一样，今年的型号没有配备交流电源适配器，因此您可能需要准备一个东西。 If you plan on going all-in on wireless charging, you can take advantage of the best MagSafe technology with the many accessories to choose. We&#39;ve tested out some of the best iPhone accessories available, from the Apple AirTag to wireless headphones to phone cases, and gathered the best ones here.</p><h2> Apple MagSafe wireless charger </h2><p><core-commerce id="17be105c44f44e2c924fc9778cb6b892" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> There are often better and cheaper alternatives to Apple&#39;s first-party accessories, but the company&#39;s <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9BcHBsZS1NSFhIM0FNLUEtTWFnU2FmZS1DaGFyZ2VyL2RwL0IwOEw1TlA2Tkc_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZWEtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjYyN2FmM2ZkLTU5NGItMzE3OS04YzEzLWJhZGYzOTQwOTBjMCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAaRxUzZ1Mh5KMgSPjBoTccOKa-8hj3LtggM_hnahkFeW&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MHXH3AM-A-MagSafe-Charger%2Fdp%2FB08L5NP6NG">MagSafe wireless charger</a> is worth considering if you have a new iPhone. Like all other MagSafe accessories, this charging pad uses magnets to attach to the back of the latest iPhones and it&#39;s surprisingly strong. Not only can you safely pick up your handset and use it with the disk still attached, but the iPhone can dangle by the charger&#39;s cord without falling off. (You still probably shouldn&#39;t do this.)</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> The charging plate itself is about a quarter-inch thick so it barely adds any heft to the iPhone. The magnets only attach to the latest iPhones, but it will still charge older models wirelessly, going back to the iPhone 8. I only wish the cable were longer than three feet so that you had more leeway to use your iPhone on the couch or in bed while powering it up.</p><p> Apple&#39;s MagSafe charger accessory comes in at $39 (although we&#39;ve seen it go on sale a few times), but if you want to spend a bit less, <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAW7_RLl0A0JotuPt2TK6AQhpSeA4qI36-2JHt1G3f1jM&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSpigen-ArcField-Magnetic-Wireless-Compatible%2Fdp%2FB08K3YZ535">Spigen&#39;s $25 ArcField magnetic wireless charger</a> is a decent dupe. It&#39;s magnets are nowhere near as strong as those on the Apple MagSafe charger — so you <em>definitely</em> shouldn&#39;t pick up your iPhone by this cable — but it&#39;ll power up your handset and stay put while doing so.</p><h2> Mophie 4-in-1 wireless charging mat </h2><p><core-commerce id="6edfc614874b47caa801fe562bc2b9f7" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> You may have accumulated a number of devices that support wireless charging at this point and <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9XaXJlbGVzcy1DaGFyZ2luZy1tYXQtd2lyZWxlc3NseS1BZGRpdGlvbmFsL2RwL0IwOExLR1FMUkM_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZWEtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjYyN2FmM2ZkLTU5NGItMzE3OS04YzEzLWJhZGYzOTQwOTBjMCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAchYGzRJBwZ2OOHfeLdJan63LYTk2jS-gtduRrOAuBul&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FWireless-Charging-mat-wirelessly-Additional%2Fdp%2FB08LKGQLRC">Mophie&#39;s 4-in-1 charging mat</a> is an easy way to power them all. It&#39;s an 11-by-8-inch rectangle with four spaces for different items to charge simultaneously. Two of those spots are large enough to accommodate smartphones while the other two in the center are smaller and fit things like AirPods perfectly. It also has an optional attachment for an Apple Watch, which means it could actually charge up to five devices at the same time.</p><p> I found the mat useful as a charging hub, turning to it each night to charge my iPhone, Apple Watch and AirPods Pro. It&#39;s worth noting that both my iPhone and my AirPods Pro live in cases, and I didn&#39;t have to remove either in order to charge them with Mophie&#39;s mat. But while the mat&#39;s size allows it to do a lot at once, it&#39;s also tough to find a big enough spot for it. It&#39;ll fit on most nightstands, but you may have to rearrange things first. Mophie has a <a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAT46VUufj25sSGTR9Yr5BxausC-Ai1oAEntGuZcpGELr&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FMophie-Wireless-Charge-Pad-Charging%2Fdp%2FB07XPWD4WW">3-in-1 wireless charging station</a> that takes up less space and has dedicated spots for your iPhone, Apple Watch and AirPods.</p><h2> AirPods </h2><p><core-commerce id="e58893eae71e42ddacd6b18f2709315d" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> It&#39;s well known now that <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:5;pos:1;pdid:AirPods" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAR1Pa6NVec4AzeK1OfMVinbGn10QkODxJvyhcB9I5ayh&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MME73AM-A-AirPods-3rd-Generation%2Fdp%2FB09JQL3NWT" data-demonetize-referrer="https://amzn.to/3p6Vfq0" class="rapid-with-clickid">Apple AirPods</a> are the best wireless earbuds for those with iPhones. Apple made its standard <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/apple-airpods-review-2021-160026883.html">AirPods</a> even better with the introduction of the third-generation models, which have an improved design, noticeably better sound and longer battery life. We appreciate the new “contoured” design, which is way more comfortable than previous AirPods, and the H1 chipset makes features like hands-free Siri and speedy pairing and switching between iPhone, iPad, and Mac possible. They&#39;re well worth their $179 price tag — but if that&#39;s a bit steep for you, <a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:7;pos:1;pdid:Beats’ new Studio Buds" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9CZWF0cy1TdHVkaW8tQ2FuY2VsbGluZy1FYXJidWRzLUJ1aWx0LUJsdWV0b290aC1IZWFkcGhvbmVzL2RwL0IwOTZTVjhTSkc_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8tZWEtMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjYyN2FmM2ZkLTU5NGItMzE3OS04YzEzLWJhZGYzOTQwOTBjMCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAQ9LvBSGa4qV7SHcGH882yt1SzIBrwGmfsfC0ZSdmsc1&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FBeats-Studio-Cancelling-Earbuds-Built-Bluetooth-Headphones%2Fdp%2FB096SV8SJG" data-demonetize-referrer="https://amzn.to/31aH5Me" class="rapid-with-clickid">Beats&#39; new Studio Buds</a> are a<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/beats-studio-buds-review-150014566.html">good alternative</a> . At $150, they have the same H1 chip inside along with balanced sound that doesn&#39;t sacrifice the punchy bass that Beats devices are known for.</p><h2> Anker Nano II 45W GaN charger </h2><p><core-commerce id="a3c7cbf8efc14487b67b2c95b80b0b37" data-type="product-list"></core-c